# Sweet Media Platform ‚Äî Architecture Reference

Use this as the source of truth when answering any question about this monorepo's setup, apps, infrastructure, or deployment.

---

## Monorepo

- **Package manager**: pnpm 10.33.2 (`packageManager` field in root `package.json`)
- **Build orchestration**: Turborepo 2.9.7 (`turbo.json` ‚Äî tasks: `build`, `dev`, `lint`, `typecheck`)
- **Workspace globs**: `apps/*`, `packages/*` (`pnpm-workspace.yaml`)
- **Root scripts**:
  - `pnpm dev` ‚Üí `turbo dev --filter=!@sweetmedia/client-template`
  - `pnpm build` ‚Üí `turbo build --filter=!@sweetmedia/client-template`
  - `pnpm new-client` ‚Üí `node scripts/setup-new-client.mjs`
  - `pnpm scaffold-client` ‚Üí `node scripts/scaffold-client-app.mjs`

