## Admin System

- Every client app has `src/app/admin/layout.tsx` wrapping with `AdminGuard` + `AdminChrome`
- `AdminGuard`: checks `useAuth` ‚Üí redirects unauthenticated to `/admin/login`
- Auth: Supabase Auth session; `isAdmin` requires row in `admin_users` for JWT email
- Admin pages are thin wrappers importing views from `@sweetmedia/admin-core`
- `AdminChrome brandName` / `brandInitial` are the only brand-specific values in admin layout
- Sidebar: uses Remix Icon (`ri-*-line`), Cormorant Garamond for brand initial

---

## SEO / Tracked Pages

- **Post-build**: `scripts/sync-tracked-pages.ts` scans `src/app/**/page.tsx`, derives routes, upserts `tracked_pages` (requires `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY`)
- **Runtime**: `resolveTrackedPageMetadata` merges Next `generateMetadata` with DB `seo_title` / `meta_description`; cache TTL via `TRACKED_PAGE_METADATA_CACHE_SECONDS` (default 15s)
- **On-demand**: `src/app/api/admin/sync-pages/route.ts` (service role)

