## Scripts

### `scripts/setup-new-client.mjs`
Full Supabase provisioning: project create ‚Üí schema ‚Üí seed ‚Üí bucket ‚Üí secrets ‚Üí Edge function deploy ‚Üí scaffold Next app ‚Üí pnpm install.

Key flags: `--slug`, `--name`, `--url`, `--region` (default us-east-1), `--org`, `--admin-email`, `--ref` (existing project: skip schema/seed/storage), `--no-scaffold`, `--force-scaffold`, `--no-brand-replace`, `--skip-pnpm`

### `scripts/scaffold-client-app.mjs`
Copy `client-template` ‚Üí `apps/<slug>`, set package name, rewrite `next.config.ts` Supabase hostname, write `.env.local`, optional `replaceBrandStrings`.

Exports: `runScaffold(opts)`, `parseApiKeysResponse(raw)`

### `scripts/migrate-wordpress-content.mjs`
WP REST API ‚Üí pull posts ‚Üí Markdown ‚Üí images to Supabase storage ‚Üí `blog_posts` upsert ‚Üí `migration-report-<site-id>.json`

### `scripts/scaffold-wp-pages.mjs`
Migration report ‚Üí stub Next.js `src/app/[route]/page.tsx` + `src/views/...` files

### `scripts/visual-audit-wp.mjs`
Playwright screenshots + computed design token JSON from live WP site

### `scripts/extract-wp-design-tokens.mjs`
Fetch WP CSS ‚Üí Elementor/globals token JSON

