## Known Issues / Drift

1. **`client-template-schema.sql` column drift**: `blog_queue` and `internal_links` in SQL differ from `admin-core` TS types and Edge Functions. Live DBs are ahead of the checked-in SQL.
2. **Edge functions not in setup script**: `process-blog-queue`, `auto-publish-approved-drafts`, `blog-webhook`, etc. exist on disk but are not deployed by `setup-new-client.mjs`.
3. **`autoInternalLinks` static mappings**: hardcoded for Sweet Media agency routes; other client brands should use DB-only `internal_links` rows.
4. **Vercel env push not scripted**: `.env.local` is written by scaffold but Vercel project creation + env var push is still manual. Vercel API script not yet built.
5. **`cipher-billing` migration in progress**: many pages still have WP/Elementor artifacts; treat as active worksite.
